<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GeoMeasure Pro - Professional Land Measurement Tools</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Advanced land measurement calculator with multiple unit conversions, mapping tools, and professional reporting">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.9.4/leaflet.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #2e7d32;
      --primary-light: #4caf50;
      --primary-dark: #1b5e20;
      --secondary: #ff9800;
      --secondary-dark: #f57c00;
      --dark: #263238;
      --darker: #1a2327;
      --light: #f5f5f5;
      --lighter: #fafafa;
      --gray: #607d8b;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      --transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
    }
    
    body {
      background-color: var(--lighter);
      color: var(--dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
      flex: 1;
    }
    
    /* Header */
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark), var(--primary));
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 1rem 0;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }
    
    .header-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--white);
    }
    
    .logo i {
      color: var(--secondary);
    }
    
    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    
    nav a {
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: var(--transition);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    
    nav a:hover, nav a.active {
      background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    
    .mobile-menu-btn {
      display: none;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    
    /* Main Click Bar */
    .main-click-bar {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 15px 25px;
      margin: 40px 0 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    
    .main-click-bar:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }
    
    .main-click-bar h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .main-click-bar .arrow {
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    
    .main-click-bar.active .arrow {
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }
    
    /* Calculator Content */
    .calculator-content {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 0;
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s, padding 0.3s;
    }
    
    .calculator-content.active {
      padding: 30px;
      max-height: 5000px;
    }
    
    /* Field Diagram Section */
    .field-diagram-bar {
      background: var(--light);
      color: var(--primary);
      padding: 12px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    
    .field-diagram-bar:hover {
      background-color: #e0e0e0;
    }
    
    .field-diagram-content {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      padding: 0;
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .field-diagram-content.active {
      max-height: 500px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .field-rep {
      font-family: monospace;
      white-space: pre;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 15px 0;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    
    /* Calculator Form */
    .calculator-header {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    
    .calculator-header h2 {
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .calculator-header p {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    
    .input-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .input-group {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .input-group h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .input-group h3 i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    
    .input-group p {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    input[type="number"], select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: var(--transition);
      background-color: var(--lighter);
    }
    
    input[type="number"]:focus, select:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.1);
      background-color: var(--white);
    }
    
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: #eee;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    
    .checkbox-group {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .checkbox-group input {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      accent-color: var(--primary);
    }
    
    .checkbox-group label {
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    
    .btn {
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: var(--white);
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: var(--transition);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary-dark);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background-color: var(--secondary);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background-color: var(--secondary-dark);
    }
    
    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .btn-group .btn {
      flex: 1;
    }
    
    .results {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 25px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
    }
    
    .results h3 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .result-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    
    .result-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .result-label {
      font-weight: 500;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .result-value {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--primary);
    }
    
    /* Map Container */
    .map-container {
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    
    #map {
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }
    
    /* Tools Section */
    .section-header {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    
    .section-header:hover {
      color: var(--primary-dark);
    }
    
    .section-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    
    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 25px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
      transition: var(--transition);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }
    
    .card h4 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    .card p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: var(--gray);
      flex-grow: 1;
    }
    
    .card .features {
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .card .features li {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      color: var(--gray);
    }
    
    .card .btn {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    
    /* Company Info */
    .company-info {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .company-info h4 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .company-info p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .contact-methods {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .contact-method {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: #f0f7f1;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    
    .contact-method:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    
    .contact-method i {
      margin-right: 10px;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background-color: var(--darker);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 60px 0 20px;
      margin-top: 80px;
    }
    
    .footer-container {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    
    .footer-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .footer-logo i {
      color: var(--secondary);
    }
    
    .footer-about p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #b0bec5;
    }
    
    .social-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
    }
    
    .social-links a {
      color: var(--white);
      background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    
    .social-links a:hover {
      background-color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    
    .footer-column h4 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--secondary);
    }
    
    .footer-column ul {
      list-style: none;
    }
    
    .footer-column ul li {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    
    .footer-column ul li a {
      color: #b0bec5;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: var(--transition);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    
    .footer-column ul li a:hover {
      color: var(--secondary);
      padding-left: 5px;
    }
    
    .footer-bottom {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #455a64;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #b0bec5;
    }
    
    .footer-bottom a {
      color: #b0bec5;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    
    .footer-bottom a:hover {
      color: var(--secondary);
    }
    
    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .header-container {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 15px;
      }
      
      nav ul {
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 100%;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      
      nav ul.show {
        display: flex;
      }
      
      .mobile-menu-btn {
        display: block;
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        right: 20px;
      }
      
      .input-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      
      .btn-group {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
    
    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    
    .fade-in {
      animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease forwards;
    }
    
    /* Print Styles */
    @media print {
      header, footer, .sidebar, .btn {
        display: none;
      }
      
      .calculator-content {
        max-height: none;
        padding: 0;
      }
      
      .results {
        border: none;
        background: none;
        padding: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container header-container">
      <a href="#" class="logo">
        <i class="fas fa-ruler-combined"></i>
        <span>GeoMeasure Pro</span>
      </a>
      
      <button class="mobile-menu-btn" id="mobileMenuBtn">
        <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
      </button>
      
      <nav>
        <ul id="navMenu">
          <li><a href="#calculator" class="active"><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Calculator</a></li>
          <li><a href="#tools"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Tools</a></li>
          <li><a href="#resources"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> Resources</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <!-- Calculator Section -->
    <section id="calculator" class="fade-in">
      <div class="main-click-bar" id="mainClickBar">
        <h1><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Land Area Calculator</h1>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down arrow"></i>
      </div>
      
      <div class="calculator-content" id="calculatorContent">
        <div class="calculator-header">
          <h2>Professional Land Measurement</h2>
          <p>Enter the measurements of opposite sides of your field. The calculator will find the average of each pair of opposite sides, convert to the traditional measurement system, and calculate the area in multiple units.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="field-diagram-bar" id="fieldDiagramBar">
          <span><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i> Field Diagram</span>
          <i class="fas fa-chevron-down arrow"></i>
        </div>
        
        <div class="field-diagram-content" id="fieldDiagramContent">
          <div class="field-rep">
            u
            ━━━━━━━━━ 
            y ┃          ┃ x
            y ┃          ┃ x
            y ┃          ┃ x
            ━━━━━━━━━ 
            v
          </div>
          <p>Simplified field representation showing opposite sides</p>
          
          <div class="map-container">
            <div id="map"></div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-center"><small>Click on the map to mark your field boundaries</small></p>
        </div>
        
        <form id="calculatorForm">
          <div class="input-row">
            <div class="input-group">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler"></i> Side y</h3>
              <input type="number" id="y" step="any" placeholder="Enter length" class="input-field">
            </div>
            
            <div class="input-group">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler"></i> Side x (opposite y)</h3>
              <input type="number" id="x" step="any" placeholder="Enter length" class="input-field">
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="input-row">
            <div class="input-group">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler"></i> Side v</h3>
              <input type="number" id="v" step="any" placeholder="Enter length" class="input-field">
            </div>
            
            <div class="input-group">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler"></i> Side u (opposite v)</h3>
              <input type="number" id="u" step="any" placeholder="Enter length" class="input-field">
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="divider"></div>
          
          <div class="input-row">
            <div class="input-group">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-ruler-combined"></i> Measurement Unit</h3>
              <select id="unit" class="input-field">
                <option value="1">Meter</option>
                <option value="2">Feet</option>
                <option value="3">Gattha</option>
                <option value="4">Yard</option>
                <option value="5">Chain</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            
            <div class="input-group">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-tags"></i> Project Name</h3>
              <input type="text" id="projectName" placeholder="Optional project name" class="input-field">
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="divider"></div>
          
          <div class="input-group">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i> Additional Conversions</h3>
            <div class="input-row">
              <div class="checkbox-group">
                <input type="checkbox" id="showAcre" checked>
                <label for="showAcre">Show in Acres</label>
              </div>
              <div class="checkbox-group">
                <input type="checkbox" id="showHectare" checked>
                <label for="showHectare">Show in Hectares</label>
              </div>
              <div class="checkbox-group">
                <input type="checkbox" id="showSqft">
                <label for="showSqft">Show in Square Feet</label>
              </div>
              <div class="checkbox-group">
                <input type="checkbox" id="showSqm">
                <label for="showSqm">Show in Square Meters</label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="btn-group">
            <button type="button" class="btn" onclick="calculateArea()">
              <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Calculate Area
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="resetForm()">
              <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Reset
            </button>
          </div>
          
          <div class="results" id="output">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> Calculation Results</h3>
            <p>Enter your field dimensions and click "Calculate Area"</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="btn-group" id="exportButtons" style="display: none;">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="exportToPDF()">
              <i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> Export to PDF
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="exportToCSV()">
              <i class="fas fa-file-csv"></i> Export to CSV
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="printResults()">
              <i class="fas fa-print"></i> Print Results
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Tools Section -->
    <section id="tools" class="expanded-section fade-in">
      <div class="section-header" onclick="toggleSection('toolsContent', 'toolsArrow')">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> Professional Measurement Tools</h3>
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down arrow" id="toolsArrow"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="section-content" id="toolsContent" style="display: none;">
        <div class="card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-calculator"></i> Advanced Area Calculator</h4>
          <p>Precision area calculations for any shape with support for multiple geometric formulas and unit systems.</p>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Support for 10+ geometric shapes</li>
            <li>Custom coordinate input</li>
            <li>Save and load calculations</li>
            <li>Project management</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="btn" onclick="scrollToCalculator()">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Launch Calculator
          </button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i> GIS Map Converter</h4>
          <p>Professional-grade GIS tools for coordinate conversion and map format transformation.</p>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Convert between 20+ coordinate systems</li>
            <li>Support for GeoJSON, KML, Shapefile</li>
            <li>Batch processing of multiple files</li>
            <li>Metadata preservation</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="btn" onclick="showComingSoon()">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Launch Map Tools
          </button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i> Professional Unit Converter</h4>
          <p>Comprehensive unit conversion system with 100+ measurement units across 15 categories.</p>
          <ul class="features">
            <li>Real-time currency conversion</li>
            <li>Custom unit creation</li>
            <li>Calculation history</li>
            <li>Mobile-friendly interface</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="btn" onclick="showComingSoon()">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Launch Converter
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Resources Section -->
    <section id="resources" class="expanded-section fade-in">
